OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776330350
OL,3,CPM to meet social media bosses in
OL,4,CDowning Street after calls for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer will
OL,8,Fsummon senior figures from TikTok, X,
OL,9,FMeta and other social media giants to
OL,10,FDowning Street, urging them to do more
OL,11,Fto protect children as the government
OL,12,Fweighs new restrictions.
OL,14,FStarmer said the talks on Thursday
OL,15,Fwill be about "making sure social
OL,16,Fmedia companies step up and take
OL,17,Fresponsibility" as failing to act
OL,18,Fwould have "stark" consequences.
OL,26,@wD@OOUyD@OO]zD@LOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
