FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776330350
OL,3,CPM to meet social media bosses in
OL,4,CDowning Street after calls for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FIt comes as MPs on Wednesday rejected
OL,8,Fcalls for a default ban on children
OL,9,Faccessing social media for a second
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FSenior leaders from Mark Zuckerberg's
OL,13,FMeta, Elon Musk's X, Snap, TikTok, and
OL,14,FGoogle, which owns YouTube, will be
OL,15,Fquestioned by Starmer and Technology
OL,16,FSecretary Liz Kendall on what they are
OL,17,Fdoing to protect children and respond
OL,18,Fto parental concerns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776330350
OL,3,CPM to meet social media bosses in
OL,4,CDowning Street after calls for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FAhead of the meeting, Starmer said:
OL,8,F"Social media shapes how children see
OL,9,Fthemselves, their friendships and the
OL,10,Fworld around them. When that comes
OL,11,Fwith real risks, looking the other way
OL,12,Fis not an option.
OL,14,F"Parents rightly expect action and
OL,15,Ffast. That's why we've already taken
OL,16,Fthe powers needed to move quickly once
OL,17,Four consultation ends.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776330350
OL,3,CPM to meet social media bosses in
OL,4,CDowning Street after calls for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,F"I will take whatever steps necessary
OL,8,Fto keep children safe online. Today is
OL,9,Fabout making sure social media
OL,10,Fcompanies step up and take
OL,11,Fresponsibility.
OL,13,F"The consequences of failing to act
OL,14,Fare stark. We owe it to parents, and
OL,15,Fto the next generation, to put
OL,16,Fchildren's safety first ` because they
OL,17,Fwon't forgive us if we don't."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
