OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776330350
OL,3,CPM to meet social media bosses in
OL,4,CDowning Street after calls for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FThe government is under pressure to
OL,8,Ffollow Australia's lead, which
OL,9,Fintroduced a full ban on under-16-year-
OL,10,Folds using social media in December
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FAustralia's ban includes: Instagram,
OL,14,FFacebook, TikTok, X, Snapchat,
OL,15,FThreads, YouTube, Reddit and streaming
OL,16,Fplatforms Kick and Twitch.
OL,18,FWhen the ban came into force, under-
OL,19,F16s became unable to create new
OL,20,Faccounts, and those with existing ones
OL,21,Fsaw them deactivated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
