CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776330350
OL,3,CPM to meet social media bosses in
OL,4,CDowning Street after calls for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FThe Lords must again consider the
OL,8,FCommons' position before the Bill
OL,9,Fbecomes law, and peers could continue
OL,10,Fthe stand-off between the two Houses.
OL,12,FAs part of the Children's Wellbeing
OL,13,Fand Schools Bill, ministers are set to
OL,14,Fgain a flexible power to curb
OL,15,Fchildren's social media use with
OL,16,Fcurfews, scrolling limits and
OL,17,Frestrictions on location sharing.
OL,19,FThe government could also choose to
OL,20,Fblock under-16s from specified
OL,21,Fplatforms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
