PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776330350
OL,3,CPM to meet social media bosses in
OL,4,CDowning Street after calls for under-
OL,5,C16s ban
OL,7,FStarmer has previously been hesitant
OL,8,Fto support an outright ban but has
OL,9,Fsignalled he will take action to curb
OL,10,Ffeatures such as infinite scrolling
OL,11,Fthat keep young users hooked to social
OL,12,Fmedia.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FThe government is in the middle of
OL,20,Fconducting a consultation into young
OL,21,Fpeople's social media use.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
